# Netlify redirects file for handling CORS proxying

# Proxy for Google Places API
/maps-api/* https://maps.googleapis.com/:splat 200

# Google Places API proxy to avoid CORS
/api/google-places/*  https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/place/:splat  200

# Handle CORS headers
/api/google-places/*  https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/place/:splat  200  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *

# Fallback for SPA routing
/*  /index.html  200